WEBVTT

00:11.411 --> 00:12.344
Guys.

00:12.411 --> 00:14.311
Give us a hand.

00:15.311 --> 00:17.545
Your end.

00:17.611 --> 00:20.678
1... 2... 3. 1... 2... 3. Go.

00:25.178 --> 00:26.711
Bobby, i'll be right back.

00:28.000 --> 00:34.074
